    </section></div><div id="block274" class="block-wrapper"><section class="landing-block g-pt-20 g-pb-20">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">

			<div class="col-md-5 order-2 order-md-1 g-mb-15 g-mb-0--md">
				<img class="landing-block-node-img img-fluid g-mb-30" src="https://cdn.bitrix24.com/b8467327/landing/eb2/eb2cae77a811fd81b228e2be5064cefe/health1.jpg" alt="HEALTH&nbsp;" data-fileid="90" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}">

				<h3 class="landing-block-node-title text-uppercase g-font-weight-700 g-font-size-18 g-color-black g-mb-20">HEALTH </h3>
				<div class="landing-block-node-text"><p class="mb-0"><br></p></div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-7 order-1 order-md-2 g-mb-15 g-mb-0--md">
				<div aria-multiselectable="true">
					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-medical-019 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">School health </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">School health remains one of our core areas of intervention as schools provide an ideal platform for reaching a wider group of people within a particular setting thus making the school based interventions both economical and effective. At all times we work within the GoK structures to deliver our intervention. We work with the line ministries i.e. the County Health management teams, the County Directors of Education, the Administration, The ministry of Agriculture, the children’s department in ensuring pupils within schools receive best of services. 
</p><p class="mb-0">In 2018 we did support the Sub counties of Muhoroni and Nyando who reached to undertake Vitamin A supplementation to over 4321 pupils and offered deworming (Albendazole) to 8,702 pupils in 23 primary schools located within Kisumu Counties.  
</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-medical-060 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Maternal and Child health</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">Late entry into antenatal care after the first trimester (85%) often leads to the mother missing out on early screening for preventable illnesses, appropriate health education, micronutrient supplementation and also makes it impossible to achieve the required minimum number of ANC contacts. Poor retention in ANC through the pregnancy attributable to lack of real time data and accountability at all levels.
</p><p class="mb-0">Inadequate capacity of health facilities to offer quality ANC services with over 80% unable to provide full ANC profile hence unable to adequately identify high risk pregnancies. Significant number of home deliveries with no efforts for community mobilisation for early ANC and hospital delivery, high number of children born with low weight and preterm deliveries and still births are among the push factors that make us feel the need to intervene within this sector. 
</p><p class="mb-0">TAF will continue to engage with the respective partners to ensure that interventions are reached and the alarming trend is turned around. 
</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-medical-048 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">HIV prevention care and Support         </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">Western Kenya continues to register alarming trends as far as HIV/Aids is concerned, the ever increasing rate if new infection especially among the youth and adolescent, low condom uptake and use, HIV/IADs related mortalities are factors that we cannot just sit back and watch. We will be looking opportunities to play our part and help address the challenges being faced within the health sectors. We believe collaboration, innovation and integration of interventions can lead to success in the fight against HIV/Aids.</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-medical-036 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Water Sanitation and Hygiene</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">Access to safe water remains essential to human health and development. As the rest of the world powers towards achieving the global sustainable development agendas of which access to clean water is part of We in the global south are constantly confronted by the fact that we need to engage more towards helping our communities realize better access to clean water. This includes institutions i.e. schools where we plan to support the accessibility of clean drinking water and hygiene facilities at all levels. We have also put up three boreholes where communities are now able to access clean drinking water</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section></div><div id="block280" class="block-wrapper"><section class="landing-block g-pt-20 g-pb-20">
	<div class="container">
