				<img class="landing-block-node-img img-fluid g-mb-30" src="https://cdn.bitrix24.com/b8467327/landing/f53/f537ea485dd5b395ffc6fc7c8561d943/edu.jpg" alt="EDUCATION&nbsp;" data-fileid="100" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}">

				<h3 class="landing-block-node-title text-uppercase g-font-weight-700 g-font-size-18 g-color-black g-mb-20">EDUCATION</h3>
