				<div aria-multiselectable="true">
					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-education-002 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">OVC Educational Support Program</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0"> <span style="font-size: 1rem;">The Orphans need help, this is a reality to us when we are confronted with a huge number of request from needy pupils who are faced with the challenge of missing out on their education due luck of minor things or schools feels thus threatening their entire lives. We have intervened in providing schools fees support to nine (9) children in primary schools, supported 5 pupils in high school and have 2 currently enrolled in higher learning institutions. The demand for help is more than we can currently cater for hence the need for us to partner with like-minded institutions in ensuring nobody who wants to pursue his/her education is left behind. We believe education unlocks the potential of many children and empowers them to face the future that is more promising with education.  </span></p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;"> *</span>   In Kenya, the situation of Orphans and Vulnerable Children (OVCs) is an issue of concern. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*</span>    Currently it is estimated that there are over 3 million Orphans in the country, 47 percent orphaned as a result of HIV and AIDS and many more remain vulnerable due to several other factors. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*   </span>The statistics surrounding the rising population and the immense suffering of these children can be overwhelming. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*    </span>Over 25% of the population live on less than $2 per day and 12-15% of households in Kenya are headed by an orphan sibling. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><br></p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-education-143 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Students Exchange programs</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">TAF has global perspective and representation right from the board of directors who are well grounded within their areas of expertise and come in handy in helping the organization build its network and partnerships with institution across the globe. We have embarked on a partnership path that will see us host a number of students and professionals from oversee institution who will be coming both to learn and also offer their expertise to us all for the benefit of the communities that we serve.  </p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-education-009 u-line-icon-pro" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Internship programs          </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">Leveraging from the availability of institutions around our areas of operation we will ensure continued close working relation with the institutions to ensure that the students from the institutions get a chance and placement for their hands on experience during their time of studies. Our staffs are willing and ready to be of help in capacity building the students and sharpen them for the labour market. Internship opportunities can be accessed through our HR office where one only needs to send a request will be guided further engagement. </p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					
				</div>
