</section></div><div id="block282" class="block-wrapper"><section class="landing-block g-pt-20 g-pb-20">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">

			<div class="col-md-5 order-2 order-md-1 g-mb-15 g-mb-0--md">
				<img class="landing-block-node-img img-fluid g-mb-30" src="https://cdn.bitrix24.com/b8467327/landing/2f0/2f0ee02efea95276d6e1354faf03f1ac/community.jpg" alt="COMMUNITY EMPOWERMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY&nbsp;" data-fileid="102" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}">

				<h3 class="landing-block-node-title text-uppercase g-font-weight-700 g-font-size-18 g-color-black g-mb-20">COMMUNITY EMPOWERMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY </h3>
				<div class="landing-block-node-text"> </div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-7 order-1 order-md-2 g-mb-15 g-mb-0--md">
				<div aria-multiselectable="true">
					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img fa fa-handshake-o" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Widows support programs </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">The society moves on today neglecting the plight the Widows who continue to struggle in life so as to make ends meet. TAF for has been there to offer a helping hand and be a partner to many of widows within the communities that we serve. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*   </span> In western Kenya-Many widows are subjected to suffering by the society in general and their in-laws in particular. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*   </span> In this to be a widow is often to endure a life of neglect, discrimination, harassment, loneliness, ostracism and poverty.
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*   </span> We caution on average about 20 widows per month with a monthly supply of the basic needs. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*   </span> We have a track record of having walked the journey of life with 10 widows for over 10 years and seen their kids grow, go to school and some are now pursuing their higher education. 
</p><p class="mb-0"><span style="font-weight: bold;">*    </span>Such stories gives us a reason to believe that if we give widows a chance and their families then together we coin around better futures for our societies. 
</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img fa fa-group" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Adolescent and Youth empowerment program</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">The youth continue to form core of our engagement with communities, they are a target group that needs our continues innovative interventions, as a result we believe in going to meet the youth wherever they are rather than wait for them to come to us. Through the established networks we are ensure more and more adolescent and youths are healthy, Educated and empowered.  We go to schools through character formation program and deliver sessions in schools, we organise sporting events and offer meals for them but most importantly we deliver targeted messages to them, we offer internships and employment opportunities to them when possible, we also offer career coaching sessions to help them navigate through life challenges. </p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img fa fa-group" data-pseudo-url="{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;target&quot;:&quot;_self&quot;,&quot;enabled&quot;:false}"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Family Focus program         </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">With the increasing number of families affected and by extension the children who are forced out of their homes, the ever increasing number of family divorce cases in the country from as low as 101 in 2001 to 466 in 2015 in just one court. These statistics indicate clearly that there is a growing problem in many Kenyan homes today, and that the Kenyan child is today at a higher risk of growing up in a dysfunctional or broken home than, say, 20 years ago. Families remain an important part of our societies and stronger families ensure healthy societies it is therefore our resolve to help mediate between the many family/relationship challenges that people face today. 
</p><p class="mb-0">We have set up a network of well renowned counsellors ready to help and mediate wherever and whenever challenges are faced, we want to be to let people know there is a place (TAF) you can call and get help rather than resolve to fight and killings that continue to be experienced in our societies today.	There is a call in line that is available for those in need of the services and also a drop in centre ready to help, just in 2018 alone we have received over 40 calls and helped counsel 11 families. 
</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element js-animation fadeInUp card g-brd-none">
						<div class="card-header u-accordion__header g-bg-transparent g-brd-none rounded-0 p-0">
							<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-title-link d-block text-uppercase g-pos-rel g-font-weight-700 g-brd-bottom g-brd-primary g-brd-2 g-py-15">
								<span class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img-container g-valign-middle g-font-size-23 g-mr-10 g-color-primary">
									<i class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-img icon-diamond"></i>
								</span>
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-title g-font-size-12 g-valign-middle d-inline-block">Sustainability fronts </div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="landing-block-card-accordeon-element-body">
							<div class="card-block u-accordion__body g-py-20 px-0 g-color-gray-dark-v5">
								<div class="landing-block-node-accordeon-element-text g-font-size-default"><p class="mb-0">We equally engage in projects that we that act as a learning centre for learning, we have noted that people often have the desire to do something but luck the persons to take them through the HOs to do something. We currently have a firm with 40 pigs which keep reproducing and every three months we supply to the market, we also use our produce to support the children homes as a way of giving back to the communities we serve and ensuring that they have food. 
</p><p class="mb-0">We enough land that we hope to put up three greenhouses which will be a learning centre for the community, a source of employment for a handful of youths and a source of revenue to keep our activities running. 
</p></div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section></div><div id="block304" class="block-wrapper"><section class="g-pt-60 g-pb-60 g-bg-gray-dark-v1">
